{"tid":244302,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA話當年]west係咪真係食左lbj老母","createTime":"2017-05-15T10:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T23:11:25.000Z","uid":70760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"985ff273e927b0500b04ddae2f35c6365a1b42d9","tid":244302,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:50:55.000Z","msg":"佢老母好似專揀後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wordondastreet.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/da-real-lambo-gloria-lebron-james.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwordondastreet.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F12%2Fda-real-lambo-gloria-lebron-james.jpg&h=dd8e56bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12825355ebfd4ffb5b5aef7c33797699c0559347","tid":244302,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23388bbcea4d4c6c0c58b5af60df22d32de4620","tid":244302,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T21:24:54.000Z","msg":"宜家呀west係街比人撞到好霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01def05855e982048ff9dd69de2e0b86b0bbd93d","tid":244302,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T21:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家呀west係街比人撞到好霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點霉法 話晒打過下nba 識理財應該有屋有車"},{"pid":"17ed6a2dea06c109d110ca2a50021d8bd7009915","tid":244302,"uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宜家呀west係街比人撞到好霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點霉法 話晒打過下nba 識理財應該有屋有車</blockquote><br />\n成日有新聞話NBA球員好多退休一兩年就破產"},{"pid":"30994545c6f632d08c98e751c90a12c5742899d1","tid":244302,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:18:31.000Z","msg":"佢都算係NBA界既小鮮肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係David west, James 老母應該爽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e208004259fe3acdc66970bb8eba8f512321679","tid":244302,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:30:05.000Z","msg":"大家還記得Delonte West ，這位前NBA球員曾效力包括塞爾特人、超音速、騎士和小牛在內的多支球隊。事實上他還曾是「小皇帝」LeBron James的隊友。職業生涯場均能貢獻9.7分和3.6個助攻。然而，自2012年離開小牛之後，你便沒能再回到NBA的賽場了，取而代之的是到了外國打球，這甚至包括中國的福建和上海。<br />\n<br />\n而最讓球迷熟知的，或許不是他的球技，而是一則關於他的傳聞。在2010年騎士季後賽失利後，美國媒體爆出West和LeBron James母親有染的醜聞，這甚至被好事者認為導致了James離開騎士的原因。盡管天賦不錯，但一系列的負面新聞包括在塞爾特人更衣室打架使得他無法再在NBA立足。<br />\n<br />\n無球可打的Delonte West近日被發現在休士頓街頭，看上去十分落魄。發現他的球迷坦言這令他十分難過，因為他本來是選秀首輪的球員，但現在他甚至沒有穿鞋就在街上走。當這位球迷問他是否就是Delonte West的時候，面前的男人只說「我曾經是，但我現在已經和那段生活沒有關係了。」<br />\n<br />\nTMZ試圖聯絡Delonte West，但所有方法都失敗了，連West的前經理人都無法聯繫得到。"},{"pid":"a54cbd72440533ec490fe5095ac77a0aa23f1592","tid":244302,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:30:52.000Z","msg":"「我曾經是，但我現在已經和那段生活沒有關係了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n灰成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169c20e457bbd5267f6aaa40af10b1cb2134bcce","tid":244302,"uid":91196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:34:51.000Z","msg":"點解樓主張圖係david west黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5a3e328878037bf33c5d6aad11fb5bcb908c3d","tid":244302,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:37:18.000Z","msg":"太上皇"},{"pid":"772f333c0608e2d7ee4a5a7864e0298ad550a4ec","tid":244302,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T23:11:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「我曾經是，但我現在已經和那段生活沒有關係了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n灰成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該俾人呃左錢 sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}